name: RugbyCentric
tag_list: rugby, fitness, conditionning, perfomance, training, software, organizer, performance-software
overview: RugbyCentric is a free platform designed for the rugby players of all ages and levels that want to improve their level of performance. RugbyCentric gives access to a database of rugby-specific fitness and conditionning exercises as well as articles on recovery, game preparation and technique. If you create an account, the platform provides the tools rugby players need to set their goals, design their custom training program, schedule their sessions, evaluate their peformance and monitor their progress.
